title: Modern, Brand New 1 BR w/Balcony!
posting_body: ['Are you looking for a brand new community to call home?', "Then you're in luck - Lucille would be the perfect fit for you!", 'Managed by Solhem, Lucille is located in the heart of the Northeast Arts District and just minutes from Downtown.', 'Walk your dog along the river, bike throughout the quiet NE streets, and immerse yourself in everything this neighborhood has to offer!', 'Lucille is a sister property to The Julia, located a half-block up Broadway.', 'Lucille features multiple state-of-the-art amenities including a stunning rooftop deck and efficient, upgraded unit interiors for your everyday life.', 'Plan R -- #231', 'Please note, our online pricing shows the effective monthly rate when factoring in our current specials.', 'However, you would use the special up-front and pay regular market rent $1,545/mo afterwards.', '#231 is finished with vinyl oak plank flooring and gray quartz countertops.', 'This 559 square foot 1 bedroom, 1 bathroom layout features a gray quartz breakfast bar, a spacious walk-in closet, and a private balcony.', 'Note: Photos are of a similar floor plan.', 'For your Instagram fix: @solhemcompanies', 'Lucille is managed by locally-owned Solhem Companies: <URL>', 'For more info and to apply: <URL>', 'Prices subject to change.', 'Minneapolis -- Mpls -- NE -- Northeast -- U of M -- Boutique -- Luxury -- Scandinavian -- Mid-Century Modern -- Bike Friendly -- Pet, Dog, Cat Friendly -- Green Living -- Sustainable -- Electric Car Charging -- New Construction -- Locally Owned -- Solhem']
